<div style="font-family: Georgia, arial, verdana, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 300; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 17px; widows: 1; display: block; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><font style="box-sizing: border-box;" face="Georgia" size="3"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;">We are pleased to inform you that the Payment System Data Portal will be live on<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><b style="box-sizing: border-box;">July 15, 2016</b>.&nbsp;</span></font></div>
<div style="font-family: Georgia, arial, verdana, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 300; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 17px; widows: 1; display: block; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><font style="BOX-SIZING: border-box" face="Georgia" size="3"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;">Password reset links will be emailed to all participants<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><b style="BOX-SIZING: border-box">starting from 14th of July, 2016</b>.</span></font></div>
<div style="font-family: Georgia, arial, verdana, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 300; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 17px; widows: 1; display: block; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><font style="BOX-SIZING: border-box" size="3"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="BOX-SIZING: border-box"><font face="Georgia"></font></span></font></div>
